{#- /ask/ — plan §5 (AI-native interaction), Wave 3. The dedicated concierge
    surface: server-rendered, AI-crawler-visible prose stating what Lane does
    and its honesty posture, plus the live chat (askLive) or an inert "coming
    soon" shell (fields inside <fieldset disabled>, no network path).
    ORDER (operator design fine-tune 2026-07-10): heading → the chat RIGHT
    THERE → the explainers below (kills the white space to reach the chat).
    COPY GUARD: no Rule-32 stop-list phrasing (never claim to search/access/be
